These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  entrepreneur, analyst, coach, freelancer, dressmaker, writer
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: salsa, folk, metal, trance, funk, reggae
 1. the fan of metal is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 2. the analyst is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 3. the analyst is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 4. the fan of reggae is not to the left of the coach##8
 5. the writer is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
 6. the fan of funk is somewhere between the fan of metal and the writer##7
 7. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
 8. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 9. the writer is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
10. the fan of salsa is not to the left of the freelancer##8
11. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5
12. the analyst is on the right of the freelancer##1
13. the coach is somewhere to the right of the fan of metal##5
14. the writer is somewhere between the fan of folk and the coach##7
15. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
16. the dressmaker is not the fan of trance##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Job           | freelancer | analyst | entrepreneur | dressmaker | writer | coach |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | metal    | folk  | funk  | trance            | reggae  |

