.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, reading, camping, traveling, chess
6 different pets are kept: horse, dog, hamster, rabbit, fish, rat
 1. the person who's hobby is camping is not the owner of the rat##6
 2. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
 3. the owner of the fish is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the owner of the rat is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the dog##2
 6. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
 7. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 8. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the owner of the rabbit##6
10. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
12. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
13. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
14. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
15. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Hobby   | reading | chess | rock-climbing | traveling | camping | collecting |
| Pet     | hamster  | horse  | dog         | rat | fish    | rabbit   |

