 4. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the french##8
 5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
 8. the russian is not to the right of the russian##8
 9. the pakistani is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the australian and the person who's sport is skiing##7
12. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skiing##5
13. the brazilian is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
14. the french is on the right of the russian##1
15. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is volleyball and the pakistani##7
16. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##8
17. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
18. the australian is the person who's sport is handball##1
