 7. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the british##8
 8. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the mexican##3
10. the owner of the lizard is not the chinese##6
11. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
12. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the australian##3
13. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Nationality   | german | nigerian | british  | australian     | mexican | chinese |
| Pet           | ferret        | hedgehog    | goldfish | pony | lizard     | mouse  |

