 2. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person eating kiwi##7
 3. the person eating orange is not the person drinking mirinda##6
 4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
 5. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person eating cucumber##8
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
 9. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
